222
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:18,140
Oh!

223
00:14:18,880 --> 00:14:19,660
Tady to je.

224
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,300
Aha.

225
00:14:23,420 --> 00:14:25,920
